24 Amend the bill by striking out all of section 7 and inserting the following:
25 'Sec. 7. Appropriations and allocations. The following appropriations and
26 allocations are made.
27 HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES, DEPARTMENT OF
28 Division of Licensing and Certification Z036
29 Initiative: Establishes one Comprehensive Health Planner II position, effective July 1,
30 2026, to develop program applications and implement the department's enforcement
31 requirements for charity care and other financial assistance programs required of hospitals,
32 including investigating patient complaints, taking corrective actions and providing staff
33 support for any necessary legal action. The initiative also provides funding for related All
34 Other costs.
